K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125a-14: char pa bzlog pa ni rtsva munydza'i lhas ma la lan gsum bzlas brjod byas te rtsa ba'i rig sngags kyis lan bdun btab nas mdud pa bdun dor bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125a-16: bde bar bya na chos gos kyi grvar lan gsum bzlas brjod byas te mdud pa gsum dor bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125a-17: zas dkar gsum zos la nyin zhag gsum smyung ba byas nas padma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125a-18: yungs kar dkar po la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod byas te grong ngam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125a-19: grong khyer mtshams bcad par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125a-20: rig sngags thams cad gcod par 'dod pas sna tshogs pa'i mtshon cha la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas te chu la bcad par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-0: snod gsar par chu blug nas lan bdun bzlas brjod byas te khrus byas na log 'dren @125b thams cad bcing ba byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-1: me tog dkar po dag la bzlas brjod byas te bsnan na dug med par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-2: nang thams cad la shing ka ra b'i ra'i lcug mas byab par bya ste bdag bsrung ba byas na gang du gdon gyi phyir yang las thams cad bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-6: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor du sna ma'i me tog gi 'bru mar gyi nang du aa ti mu ta ka smyugs pa'i yam sreg shing la 'gro lding ba'i rig sngags kyis btab ste lan bcu bzhir sbyin sreg bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-7: 'byung po dbab par 'dod pas ra'i 'o ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-9: shing aa pa mrga'i yam sreg shing dag la 'gro lding ba'i rig sngags btab ste lan lngar sbyin sreg bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-10: 'gro ba thams cad kyi ched du sbyin sreg bya bar 'dod pas 'bras thug po che dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-14: shing ka ra b'i ra dkar po'i yam sreg shing la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod byas te sbyin sreg byas na sems can thams cad kyi ched du sbyin sreg byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-15: rnyed par bya ba'i don du ru rta dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:125b-16: 'bru mar las 'gro lding ba'i rig sngags kyis lan bdun bzlas brjod byas te gdong bkrus nas smras na gang bslangs pa de thob par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-1: cad du'ang de bzhin gshegs pa'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-2: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten la spos dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-8: byug pa rnams kyis mchod cing ci nus kyis lha bshos kyang dbul bar bya ste bsrung ba dang bcas cho ga dang bcas pas mi mjed kyi sems can thams cad bsrungs par gyur cig sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-11: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-12: gzhon nu sgra gcan zin dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-13: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-17: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rangs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-19: 'phags pa me kha la zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-20: rgya gar gyi mkhan po pradzny'a war ma dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-004:126a-21: zhus chen gyi lotstsha ba bande ye shes snge la sogs pas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa ////
